Since the birth of the world's first university in a modern sense, universities have shouldered a unique mission different from other social organizations. For Chinese universities, which rose in the autumn of national crisis, their spirit is deeply affected by traditional culture and the changes of the times, advocating the value concept of "serving the world with virtue, cultivating Qi and governing peace" and the patriotic responsibility of "building a strong country with learning."
At present, the trend of informatization and internationalization of higher education is becoming increasingly obvious, and the global competition in education, science and technology, and talent is intensifying. As an important "supply side," the structural reform of higher education is facing unprecedented opportunities and challenges.
In particular, the proposal of the overall plan for comprehensively promoting the construction of world-class universities and first-class disciplines not only shows China's confidence and determination to move forward from a large country of higher education to a powerful country of higher education, but also puts forward higher and newer requirements for the development of universities.
How can we strive to become one of the most popular universities in the world in a relatively short time, speed up the construction of several world-class universities and a number of world-class disciplines on the basis of a certain gap, and realize "overtaking on corners"?
In addition to firm goal confidence, path confidence and ability confidence, colleges and universities should also give full play to three advantages: first, the late development advantage, through the continuous introduction of overseas outstanding academic talents, learning from the advanced experience of world-class universities, to achieve a significant improvement in academic level and school running quality; Second, cultural advantages, inherit the wisdom connotation accumulated by Chinese civilization in the past five thousand years, carry forward and develop excellent traditional culture, so as to condense strength, shape brand and improve image; Third, institutional advantages, give full play to the institutional advantages of socialist countries, strengthen goal driving, pool consensus and joint efforts, optimize resource allocation, and provide a sustainable and solid guarantee for schools to accelerate catching up with and surpass the world's advanced level.
In particular, we should be aware that it is impossible to build a world-class university with thousands of schools. Each school must show its personality and characteristics while giving full play to its advantages.
School running characteristics should not only have common Chinese characteristics, but also reflect their own unique goal orientation, school running tradition and resource endowment.
As far as Zhejiang University is concerned, we pay attention to highlighting the characteristics of three aspects in running the school: first, highlight the training characteristics of innovative and entrepreneurial talents, build an integrated education environment integrating science and education and combining schools and enterprises, and form a full chain entrepreneurship education ecosystem; Second, highlight the characteristics of interdisciplinary convergence, promote the optimization and adjustment of discipline system, create an institutional environment for interdisciplinary, and actively cultivate interdisciplinary emerging disciplines and landmark interdisciplinary achievements; Third, highlight the school running system and social service characteristics, carry out in-depth international exchanges and cooperation, and accelerate the formation of the pan Zhejiang University industry university research cooperation system.
In this process, it is particularly important to always adhere to the university spirit and let the university spirit resonate with the spirit of the times.
For Zhejiang University, the motto of "seeking truth and innovation," the common values of "diligent study, moral cultivation, discernment and honesty" and the latest expression system of the spirit of Zhejiang University are "accepting rivers, enlightening truth and virtue, opening things to the former people, and building our country."
This is an important guarantee for the school to adhere to the correct direction of running the school, continuously accumulate cultural height and gather spiritual strength. It has rich connotation and far-reaching significance.
Among them, "hainajiang River" emphasizes the spirit of openness and inclusiveness, embodies the mind of "using the world's talents for my own use," and embodies the high-quality concept of learning from world-famous schools to educate people; "Enlightening truth and strengthening virtue" emphasizes the spirit of seeking truth and goodness, which means that universities should receive the cultivation of virtue and the encouragement of personality while pursuing truth; "People before opening things" embodies the spirit of reform and innovation, including not only the innovation of knowledge and scientific research, but also the reform and development, innovation and innovation; "Building our country" emphasizes the spirit of patriotism and dedication, and it says that universities should always share prosperity and disgrace with the national destiny.
This series of spiritual concepts and value pursuit is the soul of Zhejiang University in its 120 years of schooling.
"The wise listen to the silent, and the wise see the invisible."
Chinese colleges and universities should further base themselves on the overall situation of the cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics, deeply grasp the orientation of the times and the historical mission of higher education, and accelerate the construction of a world-class university.
At the same time, we should adhere to humanistic care and independence and freedom, and let the university spirit interact with the spirit of the times and the national spirit, so as to provide an inexhaustible driving force for the realization of national prosperity and rejuvenation and the realization of the common ideal of mankind.
