When reading out Li Lanjuan's praise, Sun Yifeng said that Professor Li Lanjuan, as a pioneer in the cause of artificial liver in China, created a unique and effective Li's artificial liver system, made a major breakthrough in the treatment of severe hepatitis and liver failure, and significantly reduced the mortality of liver failure.
